org.fujion.event

Class PropertychangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.event.Event
      • org.fujion.event.PropertychangeEvent

  • @EventType(value="propertychange")
public class PropertychangeEvent
extends Event
    A property change event. This event is sent by a component when one of its property values has changed.
